title: Augment Cache Luck

embed.description: The easy way to save screenshots, GIFs, and websites. Make everyone happy by sharing smarter, faster, and with your point crystal clear.

body: Hi guys so this is my first time posting and in general using the boards/forums, just wanted to share my luck with the Augment Cache's I got! I got bored and spent some $ on LoL because this is a free to play game :^) Anyway I'd be happy to see what other peoples luck has been like and send some pics ;) Also I'm looking for some duo partners for ranked! I'm a dirty {{champion:245}} Jungle main with 300+ games, currently sitting on Platinum 4, thanks!

replies.body: Damn you actually got some pretty nice skins there
havn't got any pics but i got dj sona twice
The luckiest I've got when it comes to multiple high priced skins is 2 Mecha Zero Sions in a row! But you got much luckier haha :)
The luckiest i got was soulstealer vayne from a forged chest from a gemstone kek
